## Next Steps for You

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 1. **Add your Razorpay test keys** to [.env](file:///c:/Users/dhruv/E-commerce-website-master-final/.env):
>    ```
>    RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=rzp_test_your_key_here
>    RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=your_secret_here
>    ```
>    Get them from [Razorpay Dashboard → API Keys](https://dashboard.razorpay.com/app/keys)
> 2. Start the dev server and **test a payment** on the checkout page
